Package: EventProjection
Title: Event Prediction in Clinical Trials with Time-to-Event Outcomes
Version: 0.1
Date: 2025-7-23
Authors@R: c(person("Haiming", "Zhou", role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
                    email = "haiming2019@gmail.com"))
Description: Provides tools to predict enrollment and event counts at either the design or analysis stage of a clinical trial using user-specified enrollment and time-to-event models via simulation. This package extends the functionality of the CRAN package EventPredInCure, offering additional flexibility and modeling capabilities.
